Dataset License Notice

This dataset package is derived from project preprocessing work based on IEEE-CIS fraud detection data.

Before publishing or redistributing this package, verify that your upload complies with the original data provider, Kaggle competition, and any institutional or project-specific licensing terms that apply to the source dataset.

The FORESIGHT project documentation and feature engineering notes included in this package may be shared for project review, but the underlying source-derived tabular data should only be redistributed where the original dataset terms allow it.
